title: Counter Culture Junior Food Truck
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Chinese, Indian, International, Thai, Mediterranean, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Asian, European, Fusion
description: An offspring of Counter Culture Restaurant. A little trailer located in a trailer park in South Austin near the all-vegan grocery store Rabbit Food Grocery. Has an all-vegan rotating menu of tacos, quesadillas and grilled sandwiches.
